&lt;li&gt;Build, optimize, and maintain data pipelines that power our business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and build out abstracted reusable data sets to be used for Business Intelligence, Marketing, and Data Science Research&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and evangelize a federated data validation framework to be used to monitor potential data inconsistencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Protect our users’ privacy and security through best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
